des: There are over 100 elements in the periodic table. Do you which elements have more electrons than others? Take this family friendly game to find out. If you're right, reward yourself with a prize (a jelly bean or an apple). If you're wrong, you can always try again.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
